        "text": "## Electrode Potential of Cu²⁺/Cu⁰\n\nThe standard electrode potential for the Cu²⁺/Cu⁰ half-reaction is **outside the scope of the NIST SRD-46 database**, which focuses on **metal–ligand stability constants** (formation constants, β values) and **ligand pKa values** in aqueous solution — not electrochemical reduction potentials.",
